<div class="authi">
<img class="authicn vm" id="authicon79286503" src="static/image/common/ico_lz.png" />
&nbsp;楼主<span class="pipe">|</span>
<em id="authorposton79286503">发表于 2014-10-28 20:30</em>
<span class="pipe">|</span>
<a href="http://bbs.rednet.cn/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=43572879&amp;page=1&amp;authorid=4113892" rel="nofollow">只看该作者</a>
